        "data": "<div class=\"alert alert-warning\"><strong>Note:</strong> please note that Liferay has renamed its Liferay Experience Could offerings to <i><strong>Liferay SaaS</strong></i> (formerly LXC) and <i><strong>Liferay PaaS</strong></i> (formerly LXC-SM).</div>\n\n<h1 class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" id=\"01H8066N1X71BMWR8KPQVMTM4A\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n\n<p>The services update for 03/14/2024 is a minor update for<strong> Search </strong>service.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1X678XQSM8P38E9Q5Z\">DXP Cloud Stack - 03/14/2024&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 588px; float: left; height: 250px;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 80.4766px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 74.4688px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.0391px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 320.016px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody valign=\"top\">\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 80.4766px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Backup</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 74.4688px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.14.0</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.0391px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.1